<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.11">
<l>toḻutāṭit tūmaṇi vaṇṇaṉuk kāṭceytu nōytīrnta</l>
<l>vaḻuvāta tolpukaḻ vaṇkurukūrc caṭakōpaṉcol</l>
<l>vaḻuvāta vāyirat tuḷḷivai pattu veṟikaḷun</l>
<l>toḻutāṭip pāṭa vallār tukkacīla milarkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those able to sing, dancing Veṟis in worship, these ten among</l>
<l>the unswerving thousand composed by Caṭakōpaṉ from liberal Kurukūr</l>
<l>of unswerving old fame, whose pain ended serving him of pure sapphire colour,</l>
<l>dancing in worship, will be free from the nature of misery.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
